               <p>Counsel for the Prosecution, MR. ALLEY.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT, stating it to be fixed to a building.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18191201-118-person1229">
                  GEORGE 
                  SLADE
